# Deploy stamp written by glowup-infra/deploy/scripts/deploy.sh on each
# fleet host after a successful git-based deploy. Untracked so it
# survives `git reset --hard staging/master`; gitignored so it doesn't
# show as dirty on dev workstations that ever happen to write one.
DEPLOYED

# secrets overlay — never commit a populated secrets.json. Per-file
# guard plus an explicit allowlist for the example template.
secrets.json
!secrets.json.example

# AGENTS.md is the session-protocol spec — household-specific (NAS
# paths, machine names), no LIFX code. It belongs in the private soe
# repo, which tracks it. Ignored here so it cannot re-enter the
# public repo if a checkout still has a local copy on disk.
AGENTS.md
